.DT
score
Discworld player help
score

Name
.SI 5
score - show your current score.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
score [brief|verbose] [stats]
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
Score gives you an indication of your current condition.
Score brief gives you the single line version.
Score verbose gives you the long version.
Score defaults to using the mode you are currently in.  If you put
theoption stats on the line it will show you your stats.  These horrible
arbitrary numbers that are used all over the place to calculate your
well being.  Useful command.
.EP

Examples:
.SI 5
> score
> score brief
> score verbose
> score stats
> score brief stats
.EI

See also
.SI 5
monitor
.EI
